<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; background: #f4f4f7; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e8449, #27ae60); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 24px; }
        .content { padding: 30px; color: #333333; line-height: 1.6; }
        .content h2 { color: #1e8449; margin-top: 0; }
        .info-box { background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #27ae60; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
        .amount { font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; color: #27ae60; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #666666; font-size: 12px; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0; }
    </style>
    <title>{{BankName}} - Money Received</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Money Received</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello {{FullName}},</h2>
            <p>You have received a money transfer to your account.</p>

            <div class="amount">
                {{Currency}} {{Amount}}
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <strong>Transfer Details:</strong><br />
                Date: {{TransactionDate}}<br />
                Sender: {{SenderName}}<br />
                Sender Account: {{SenderAccountNumberMasked}}<br />
                New Balance: {{Currency}} {{NewBalance}}<br />
                Reference Number: {{TransferReferenceNumber}}
            </div>

            <p>If you have any questions about this transfer, please contact our support team.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2025 CoreBanking. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
